  44,17,"wlqd akhtbrna wabtlyna qabl hwla' almushrikin qawm frewn, waja'ahum rasul krym, wahu musaa ealayh alslam, fakadhabuh fhlku, fhkdha nafeal baedayk 'ayuha alrswl, 'iin lam ywmnu"
